message:
I’ve implemented the dispatcher for `nsa`. You can now run the full test suite to verify correctness:

```bash
cd 19-Native-Sparse-Attention/NSA
pytest tests/test_nsa.py tests/test_nsa_with_compression.py -q
```

This will ensure both the standard and compressed NSA implementations match their references on CPU and GPU. Let me know if all tests pass!
